title: Football Player of the Week: Dwenger's Amaun Clark
text:
Football Player of the Week: Dwenger's Amaun Clark 
By Eric Dutkiewicz - 21Alive October 16, 2015 Updated Oct 16, 2015 at 12:04 PM EDT 
FORT WAYNE, Ind. (21Alive) The 21Alive/Parkview Sports Medicine Football Player of the Week is Bishop Dwenger’s Amaun Clark. 
Clark is a two-way player, but really shined in the Saints’ 20-17 win over Snider. 
Clark rushed for 203 yards and 2 touchdowns. He also caught a touchdown pass. 
Dwenger will win the Summit Athletic Conference championship Victory Bell with a win Friday against Wayne.
